docs/vision.md:30:### Primary Persona ‚Äî *The Power User (you)*
docs/vision.md:32:- **Context of use:** Daily ‚Äî morning dose logging, weekly ‚Äî reviewing outcomes, monthly ‚Äî ordering/restock, occasional ‚Äî researching a new peptide before adding it.
docs/vision.md:37:- **Behavior:** First or second peptide. Has their account created and protocol configured *by the Power User* (super admin). Does not need to understand reconstitution math ‚Äî they just see their schedule and log doses. May occasionally look up "what does this peptide do?"
docs/vision.md:38:- **Context of use:** Daily injection (habit-forming), occasional educational lookup. First reconstitution is handled with the Power User present, guided by the app's reconstitution flow.
docs/vision.md:39:- **Workarounds today:** Texting the Power User for every question. Sometimes guessing the dose. Sometimes skipping out of uncertainty.
docs/vision.md:40:- **Success for them:** Open the app, see "today: 250mcg BPC-157, left abdomen," confirm, close. Never need to know the reconstitution math. Never text the Power User asking what to do.
docs/vision.md:41:- **v1 scope note:** Delegated Participant is a *managed user* ‚Äî their protocol is configured and visible to the Power User (super admin). Self-serve newcomer onboarding (account creation, protocol setup from scratch) is a Year 2 feature.
docs/vision.md:44:- **TRT / anabolic users** ‚Äî Testosterone, HCG, AI/AR compounds sit in the same grey-market Telegram + crypto ecosystem as peptides. Same Power User persona, same vendor network, same ordering friction. The v1 architecture supports them without a separate product; v2 adds compound profiles and protocol templates.
docs/vision.md:60:4. **Multi-user that respects relationships.** Power User (super admin) creates and manages family/friend accounts, configures their protocols, and can review their adherence ‚Äî without exposing the full advanced UI to managed users. Each user sees only their own data.
docs/vision.md:65:**Sourcing module scope (v1):** The ordering integration in v1 means: structured vendor catalog, guided order composition (app composes the Telegram message), payment checklist, and inventory capture after confirmation. Full Telegram automation (bot sends messages without user action) is a v2 stretch goal. In v2, an AI Telegram response parser reads vendor confirmations and auto-updates order status and inventory ‚Äî more resilient than a scripted bot. The moat is the *closed data loop* ‚Äî order ‚Üí inventory ‚Üí dose ‚Üí log ‚Äî not just the automation.
docs/vision.md:93:- **Spreadsheets + Obsidian + Telegram + Coinbase** ‚Äî The status quo. Strong because it's *already in use* and free. Weak because the user is the integration layer.
docs/vision.md:103:- **Super admin / multi-user management.** Almost every competitor is single-user focused. The Power User managing protocols for family members from a web admin panel is a unique capability.
docs/vision.md:125:Default surfaces are dense, data-rich, and expert-friendly. Delegated Participants get a simplified view configured *by the Power User*, not a dumbed-down version of the same interface. When in doubt about a design decision, the Power User's workflow wins. **Tradeoff:** Cold-open newcomers who land on this product without a Power User guiding them will bounce. We are not optimizing for SEO-acquired strangers.
docs/vision.md:164:- **Year 1:** Word-of-mouth from the Power User's circle. No paid acquisition. No SEO push (the public reference site is a Year 2 question).
docs/vision.md:181:- The Power User opens the app every day without prompting
docs/vision.md:182:- The Power User abandons their spreadsheet and Obsidian notes for peptide logging
docs/vision.md:186:- **Personal adoption locked in.** The Power User uses it daily. Spreadsheet is decommissioned.
docs/vision.md:187:- **Family/friend adoption: 3-10 users.** Each has at least one active protocol configured by the Power User. They check in for their daily dose.
docs/vision.md:198:- **Power User stops using it within 90 days.** If the integration value isn't real for the builder, it isn't real for anyone.
docs/vision.md:207:1. **The Power User (you) will actually use what you build.** If interest fades after the build, family adoption likely fades too. *Mitigation:* personal-tool-first sequencing; ship the parts that benefit you immediately.
docs/vision.md:216:- **MEDIUM ‚Äî Personal motivation decay.** Solo project, ambitious scope. *Mitigation:* personal-tool-first slicing; ship something that helps the Power User in week 4, not month 12.
docs/vision.md:223:- **AI Telegram response parser:** AI reads vendor Telegram messages and auto-updates order status + inventory. More resilient than scripted bots; activates when v2 ordering ships.
docs/vision.md:235:5. **[RESOLVED] Multi-user architecture.** Web app with distinct user accounts. Power User is super admin with management controls ‚Äî can create users, configure their protocols, review their adherence. Each user logs in and sees only their own data. Resolved.
